{"type":"article","id":2444,"title":"李文亮微博评论备份（2020年6月20日起）","uid":6760,"topics":[1142,2523,2554,2977],"contents":"备份自：<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1139098205/Is9M7taaY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/1139098205/Is9M7taaY</a><br>\n因为2020年6月19日的本条微博评论莫名消失，疑似被删，所以我准备比较完整地备份一下，防止哪天突然没了。<br>\ntxt下载：<br>\n2020年 <a href=\"https://ia601703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.6.20~2020.6.30.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">6月</a> <a href=\"https://ia801703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.7.1~2020.7.31.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">7月</a> <a href=\"https://ia801703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.8.1~2020.8.31.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">8月</a> <a href=\"https://ia801703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.9.1~2020.9.30.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">9月</a> <a href=\"https://ia601703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.10.1~2020.10.31.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">10月</a> <a href=\"https://ia601703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.11.1~2020.11.30.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">11月</a> <a href=\"https://ia801703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2020.12.1~2020.12.31.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">12月</a><br>\n2021年 <a href=\"https://ia801703.us.archive.org/16/items/LiWenliang/2021.1.1~2021.1.31.txt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1月</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mohu.rocks/article/id-2444__sort-DESC\">建议倒序查看本帖以查看最新评论</a><br>\n<br>\n如果你只是要看每日精选评论，那我推荐你去<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/%e3%80%90cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e6%96%87%e4%ba%ae%e5%8c%bb%e7%94%9f%e7%9a%84%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e7%9a%84%e5%93%ad%e5%a2%99-5/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">